column2: AMBER HEARD IS A HUSBAND BEATER AND A BIG LIER
Amber Heard is horrible person. Her presence in any film will doom that film. Hiring her for any role is the same as condoning abuse, lying and manipulation. Oh and she is a terrible actor!
Amber has been vicious, unfair and lying.
I wouldn’t even pirate her movies.
What goes around comes around. Since Heard has decided to ruin Johnny’s life and career by all means possible, we in turn, after seeing the truth, should return the favor
I'm signing this cause Johnny Depps needs justice
